      "acceptanceCriteria": "Software must be validated under a documented QA plan with version control and regression testing covering hemolysis solver modules.",
      "rationale": "The CFD solver is under version control with documented regression tests, but the hemolysis sub-model lacks a formal QA plan. Achieved level 2 against required level 3; gap noted."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
