    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team accepted the simulation evidence at Low assurance level. Ten of thirteen credibility factors were assessed; three factors (Model inputs, Test samples, Equivalency of input parameters) were not assessed and flagged as epistemic gaps. The team judged the assessed factors sufficient for the intended use at MRL 3, noting that the unassessed factors were beyond the current project scope. Residual risk from unassessed factors was acknowledged without formal quantification.",
